    "description": "A systematic mesh refinement study was conducted across three grid levels (coarse, medium, fine) for the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry. Grid convergence index (GCI) was computed for velocity magnitude and shear stress fields at all five operating points. The study confirmed that discretization error falls within the acceptable threshold for MRL 2.",
